iles. Results of this kind further motivate the search for MRPs as a\nrobust characterization of the relation between observed ECME properties and\nstellar physical parameters can only be achieved with a large sample.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2021 05:24:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
