e, and allows for pruning irrelevant parameters using an\ninformation-based criterion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2021 08:58:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Nov 2021 08:24:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
